title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Nov 03 TH [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Thursday, 03 November 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guest is Judge Andrew Napolitano, host of Fox Business's Freedom Watch and author of the new book It Is Dangerous to Be Right When the Government Is Wrong: The Case for Personal Freedom, on the constitutionality of President Obama's executive order binge, Congress's countenancing, and how to use courts to wrest our liberties back.
